   <concept id="FAR_8_1103" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">8.1103</ph> Contract requirements.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">Contracting officers shall include the following items in each contract for leasing motor vehicles:</p>
         <ol id="d520e16" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e12">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
						            Scope of contract.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
						            Method of computing payments.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e22">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
						            A listing of the number and type of vehicles required, and the equipment and accessories to be provided with each vehicle.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e27">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
						            Responsibilities of the contractor or the Government for furnishing gasoline, motor oil, antifreeze, and similar items.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e32">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
                  
						            Unless it is determined that it will be more economical for the Government to perform the work, a statement that the contractor shall perform all maintenance on the vehicles.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e37">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(f)</ph>
                  
						            A statement as to the applicability of pertinent State and local laws and regulations, and the responsibility of each party for compliance with them.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d535e42">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(g)</ph>
                  
						            Responsibilities of the contractor or the Government for emergency repairs and services.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
